WEBVTT

00:00:06.208 --> 00:00:09.760
♪Holding hands silently
as flowers fall and winds rise♪

00:00:10.432 --> 00:00:13.536
♪Dark tresses cascade like mountains.
Dreams intertwine♪

00:00:13.536 --> 00:00:17.856
♪Painting realms, clouds in palm,
my brushwork for you♪

00:00:18.048 --> 00:00:22.112
♪Light and shadow overlap
my name across time and space♪

00:00:22.272 --> 00:00:25.960
♪Across starry rivers,
I chase dreams afar♪

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:30.624
♪Arms spread wide,
falling through heaven and earth♪

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:33.280
♪The rhythm of breath and heartbeat♪

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:38.464
♪A meeting of the souls♪

00:00:39.168 --> 00:00:43.424
♪Through shifting seas and lands,
I'd know you still♪

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:47.800
♪Eyes bright as moonlit skies,
untouched by worldly dust♪

00:00:48.032 --> 00:00:51.680
♪Smiling gazes write eternity♪

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:56.768
=The Crush=

00:00:57.235 --> 00:00:59.721
=Episode 17=
(Trap of Love Rivalry and Mother-in-law)

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:06.000
Alright, the tea offering is done.

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:08.400
I have something to tell you.

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:09.520
Mother.

00:01:10.160 --> 00:01:10.800
Please wait.

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.160
I also have an announcement to make.

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:17.120
Zixuan and I have discussed this.

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:18.160
Right now,

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.240
I am the legitimate wife

00:01:20.240 --> 00:01:22.040
of the eldest son of the Li family.

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:24.560
Therefore, I should take charge of

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:26.400
all the household affairs.

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:28.000
You can rest now.

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:28.960
Well...

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:33.640
That's only proper.

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.120
But, Zixuan,

00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:39.440
the person you've been looking for

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:42.120
has come looking for you.

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:45.160
Miss, please come in.

00:01:54.760 --> 00:01:55.560
Madam.

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:58.440
Zixuan, as your senior family member,

00:01:58.720 --> 00:02:00.480
I have the right to inquire about

00:02:00.920 --> 00:02:02.640
your taking a concubine, right?

00:02:04.520 --> 00:02:06.000
I know you've been searching

00:02:06.160 --> 00:02:07.680
for the person

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.480
who saved you at the tea mountains
all these years.

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:12.440
By a twist of fate,

00:02:12.440 --> 00:02:15.720
this person turns out
to be Miss Niaoniao.

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:18.800
When I was young, I once

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:20.440
went to pick tea in the mountains.

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:22.160
It rained heavily.

00:02:22.160 --> 00:02:23.840
I intended to find shelter,

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:25.320
but unexpectedly,

00:02:25.320 --> 00:02:27.440
I found a young gentleman drowning.

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:29.760
He seemed to be in danger,

00:02:29.920 --> 00:02:31.000
so I rescued him.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:33.120
I left

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:34.520
after the skies cleared.

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:36.760
Later, my family fell into decline

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:39.720
and I ended up at Tianxiang Tea House.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:40.960
So I never had a chance

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:42.640
to look for that young gentleman.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:45.400
Until I heard that Madam Tang

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:48.520
was searching for the person
who saved Young Master Zixuan.

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:50.600
The whole scenario

00:02:50.600 --> 00:02:52.640
sounded quite familiar.

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:54.680
No wonder

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:57.320
when I first met Young Master Zixuan,

00:02:57.480 --> 00:02:59.880
I felt an instant connection.

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:04.880
Miss Niaoniao.

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:07.280
On what date did you find me?

00:03:07.640 --> 00:03:09.200
The tenth year of the Xining era.

00:03:09.600 --> 00:03:10.520
On Qingming Festival.

00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:11.440
And where?

00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:12.880
By the Xiyu Cliff

00:03:13.160 --> 00:03:14.360
of the tea mountain.

00:03:14.920 --> 00:03:17.080
What were you wearing that day?

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.480
I wore white clothes and tied up my hair

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:20.840
for better mobility.

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:27.240
Young Master.

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:37.040
Xuan, the time, location,

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:38.120
and attire

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:41.240
all match perfectly. It can't be wrong.

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:46.000
The Li family has always
repaid the kindness.

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:48.120
Miss Niaoniao

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:50.800
has expressed her feelings.

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:52.840
She has feelings for you.

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:55.320
As your mother,

00:03:55.320 --> 00:03:56.800
I'll decide for you.

00:03:56.960 --> 00:03:58.320
Take Niaoniao as your concubine

00:03:58.320 --> 00:03:59.720
and care for her.

00:03:59.880 --> 00:04:02.920
Consider it repaying her
for saving your life.

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:04.760
Mother.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:07.440
We held the wedding ceremony yesterday,

00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:10.040
and you've already
found my husband a concubine.

00:04:10.360 --> 00:04:11.440
Isn't it inappropriate?

00:04:12.200 --> 00:04:15.400
Xiaotang, mind your words.

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:17.720
As the principal wife,

00:04:17.960 --> 00:04:19.840
you should have magnanimity.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.720
Don't lecture me about magnanimity.

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:26.760
I know exactly what's going through

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:28.040
your mind.

00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:31.720
I will not take any concubines.

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:34.560
Xuan.

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:37.880
If Miss Niaoniao hadn't saved you,

00:04:38.040 --> 00:04:39.080
you wouldn't be

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.800
standing here safe and sound.

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:44.600
The Li family has always
repaid the kindness.

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:47.040
Don't disappoint your life-saver.

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.400
This matter is settled.

00:04:56.280 --> 00:04:57.720
Are you jealous?

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:00.760
I don't care

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:02.440
if you take concubines or not.

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:05.480
My task is to make the Top Tea.

00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:07.920
You don't mind it?

00:05:10.960 --> 00:05:11.760
Not at all.

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:18.360
Then, on the wedding night...

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:22.760
I was fulfilling my obligation.

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:28.720
I just don't want

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.760
to interfere with your plans

00:05:31.400 --> 00:05:33.600
of repaying your life-saver.

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:37.920
You are jealous.

00:05:37.920 --> 00:05:38.880
No, I'm not.

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:45.080
I'm grateful that she saved me.

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:46.400
But gratitude isn't love.

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:50.320
I don't believe you.

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:53.120
Men

00:05:54.080 --> 00:05:55.480
never forget their perfect

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.480
first love.

00:05:57.880 --> 00:05:58.920
I know it very well.

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:01.360
That's not true.

00:06:05.360 --> 00:06:06.280
Aren't you into her?

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:07.840
No.

00:06:08.840 --> 00:06:09.720
You are.

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:11.520
I bet you just can't

00:06:11.520 --> 00:06:12.800
forget about Niaoniao.

00:06:22.760 --> 00:06:24.880
What's wrong? Why are you upset?

00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:26.680
I...

00:06:37.320 --> 00:06:39.000
You helped Zixuan

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:40.480
get rid of Mr. Wang.

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:43.880
And you saved him back then.

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:45.560
Truth be told,

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:48.720
you're the perfect match for Zixuan.

00:06:50.520 --> 00:06:53.080
Thank you for looking after me so much.

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:54.080
I can only

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:55.480
repay your kindness

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:57.200
by sharing your burdens.

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:05.640
This is...

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:09.360
You're a clever girl.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:12.000
You know what to do with it.

00:07:13.640 --> 00:07:15.120
Helping me

00:07:15.600 --> 00:07:17.320
means helping yourself.

00:07:17.880 --> 00:07:20.440
Get rid of Wei Xiaotang,
that thorn in our side,

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:22.600
and I swear you'll be

00:07:22.960 --> 00:07:25.120
well provided for in this household.

00:07:31.760 --> 00:07:34.480
Thank you in advance, Madam.

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:49.680
Young Master.

00:07:49.880 --> 00:07:51.440
Please save my lady.

00:07:51.440 --> 00:07:52.240
Young Master, I...

00:07:53.280 --> 00:07:54.280
What happened to her?

00:07:54.440 --> 00:07:55.280
Tell me everything.

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:56.520
My lady is

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:59.600
being harassed by a gang of thugs.

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:01.440
Those thugs are ferocious,

00:08:01.600 --> 00:08:03.040
and they keep coming back.

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:04.000
Young Master.

00:08:04.280 --> 00:08:06.240
Please help my lady in return

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:07.480
for saving your life.

00:08:07.720 --> 00:08:09.360
Please, Young Master!

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:10.840
Please.

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:12.880
Don't test my patience.

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:34.760
Miss Niaoniao.

00:08:35.040 --> 00:08:36.800
What happened here?

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:40.360
My lady.

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:43.360
That thug

00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:44.960
was Mr. Wang's associate.

00:08:45.520 --> 00:08:46.960
My lady

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:48.440
testified for the Li family.

00:08:48.560 --> 00:08:50.280
That's why she's being harassed.

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:53.480
Ning An,

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:55.760
take Miss Niaoniao's maid

00:08:56.280 --> 00:08:58.280
to purchase daily necessities.

00:08:59.040 --> 00:08:59.960
Yes, Young Master.

00:09:00.400 --> 00:09:01.520
My lady, come on.

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:03.680
After you, Miss.

00:09:15.480 --> 00:09:16.480
It's rouge.

00:09:17.800 --> 00:09:19.040
What a makeup artist.

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.160
Outside there,

00:09:23.160 --> 00:09:24.480
I paid off that man.

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:29.680
Tell me everything.

00:09:35.520 --> 00:09:37.040
Why did you go through

00:09:37.280 --> 00:09:40.320
all this trouble to stage this show?

00:09:45.200 --> 00:09:46.360
Young Master.

00:09:46.840 --> 00:09:48.360
I acted impulsively.

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:51.080
I just wanted to be closer to you.

00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:53.440
I was jealous of Miss Xiaotang.

00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:54.960
I met you

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:57.120
before she did.

00:09:57.800 --> 00:09:59.560
But now, she's the one...

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:02.640
That's why I resorted to this scheme.

00:10:03.280 --> 00:10:04.160
Young Master,

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:06.960
I'd do anything for you.

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:15.960
Love is not

00:10:16.280 --> 00:10:18.280
about who comes first.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:19.880
I will love

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:22.400
no one but Wei Xiaotang.

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:25.080
Farewell.

00:10:42.160 --> 00:10:42.760
Sister.

00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:46.560
Li Zixuan visited
Tianxiang Tea House today.

00:10:49.920 --> 00:10:50.720
Then

00:10:50.960 --> 00:10:52.600
we'll get Miss Niaoniao here

00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:53.560
tomorrow.

00:11:00.280 --> 00:11:00.760
Be careful.

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:02.880
Miss Niaoniao is moving in.

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.840
Is Young Master marrying her?

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:07.360
No way. Young Madam is so aggressive.

00:11:07.560 --> 00:11:08.360
How could she

00:11:08.360 --> 00:11:09.320
allow it to happen?

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:10.360
Don't be so sure.

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:12.040
Young Master visited

00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:13.200
Miss Niaoniao just days ago.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:13.840
Really?

00:11:13.920 --> 00:11:15.280
How dare you gossip

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.880
about your masters?

00:11:21.160 --> 00:11:23.240
- Thank you, Madam.
- Mother.

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:25.520
I made it clear yesterday.

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.760
I will run the household from now on.

00:11:28.560 --> 00:11:30.080
How could you invite

00:11:30.400 --> 00:11:31.640
a stranger to move in?

00:11:33.520 --> 00:11:35.760
Sister, don't blame Madam.

00:11:36.280 --> 00:11:37.840
She simply took pity on me

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:39.800
and couldn't bear to see me homeless.

00:11:40.280 --> 00:11:41.000
It's my fault.

00:11:41.640 --> 00:11:43.360
I moved in without cause.

00:11:43.640 --> 00:11:45.120
That's why you're upset.

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:48.280
Xiaotang, Niaoniao isn't a stranger.

00:11:48.320 --> 00:11:50.600
She saved Zixuan's life.

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:53.040
And she's being bullied out there.

00:11:53.320 --> 00:11:55.280
Since you've married into our family,

00:11:55.480 --> 00:11:57.000
uphold Zixuan's reputation.

00:11:57.440 --> 00:11:59.080
If people learn that

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:00.800
we turn a blind eye to Niaoniao,

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:03.160
what will people say about Zixuan?

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:04.320
Madam.

00:12:04.840 --> 00:12:06.320
Please don't let me cause discord

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:07.880
between you and Xiaotang.

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:10.520
If I'm unwelcome here,

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:11.880
I'll pack my belongings

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:13.000
and move out.

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:13.480
Alright.

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:16.960
Pack your things and leave now.

00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:18.760
You can hurry up

00:12:19.400 --> 00:12:20.360
and move out today.

00:12:25.080 --> 00:12:27.160
What's wrong? Reluctant to leave?

00:12:28.280 --> 00:12:29.960
Shall I send helpers to assist you?

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:30.840
Wei Xiaotang.

00:12:31.800 --> 00:12:33.760
We had Zixuan's silent approval

00:12:34.080 --> 00:12:35.840
regarding this matter.

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:37.280
Silent approval?

00:12:39.040 --> 00:12:39.960
Miss Niaoniao,

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:41.400
did Zixuan visit you

00:12:41.400 --> 00:12:43.400
at Tianxiang Tea House yesterday?

00:12:45.880 --> 00:12:47.760
Was he concerned for your safety

00:12:47.800 --> 00:12:50.200
and left Ning An there to protect you?

00:12:58.680 --> 00:13:00.400
Did he also entrust the milk tea stall

00:13:00.920 --> 00:13:02.280
to you?

00:13:02.480 --> 00:13:04.280
Who entrusted the milk tea stall to you?

00:13:05.080 --> 00:13:06.520
Calm down, Xiaotang.

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:08.640
Young Master Zixuan didn't say that.

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:09.760
I asked for it.

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:14.120
The milk tea stall is mine.

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:15.560
None of you

00:13:16.560 --> 00:13:18.400
will take it from me.